data.description: Welcome to this 3-level end unit with lower level guest suite including its own laundry. This home showcases hardwood floors on the main level and new luxury vinyl flooring on the lower level. The interior has been freshly painted, giving the space a clean and airy feel. The home has a newly installed roof (03/22/2024) with a Limited Lifetime Warranty and 5-year roofer installation warranty. In addition to a new roof, a brand new deck and front railing has also been added. Get amazing savings on energy! This Townhome features a SolarEdge Rooftop smart energy ecosystem with 30 solar panels optimized for solar power production and energy storage. The “mySolarEdge” homeowner app allows for easy monitoring of energy amounts being produced. Also, never worry about power outages as this home is equipped with a GENERAC self-regulating backup generator. There have been many more updates as well.  The home is ideally situated within a community offering lots of amenities including clubhouse access, pools, fitness center, playgrounds, hiking trails, and pet-friendly facilities. Additionally, this home is within easy walking distance of GORC park, featuring newly renovated ball fields, basketball courts, playgrounds, and pet-friendly amenities, as well as steps away from a new tot lot! Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a  property in one of Anne Arundel County's most desirable neighborhoods
